headline: Dow and Innventure to Partner on Waste-to-Value Platform
summary: Refinity, Innventure's subsidiary, will work with DOW to scale and commercialize cost-effective waste-to-value technologies, aimed at converting mixed waste.

headline: DOW Stock Down 24% in 3 Months: Should You Buy the Dip?
summary: While DOW benefits from investment in high-return projects and cost actions, weak end-market demand and declining estimates cast a pall on its prospects.
